{"tid":557192,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[獲獲新鮮獲獲甘] 8南亞男尖沙嘴街頭　劫4.5億日圓","createTime":"2018-02-11T06:11:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-12T06:41:44.000Z","uid":136455,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7d37f342c649dda618e252ea15716a0983b14543","tid":557192,"uid":136455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T06:11:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MByH9XiWwAA&amp;t=6s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMByH9XiWwAA%26t%3D6s&d=nDiTdU8cgH%2FcSBu6VtOsldr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=5e484978\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MByH9XiWwAA&amp;t=6s</a><br />\n【本報訊】尖沙嘴街頭昨晨發生4.5億日圓（約3,200萬港元）巨劫案，8名相信早有預謀南亞裔賊人，以拳頭及利刀截劫5名押款往銀行的找換店職員，搶走載有日圓的行李篋。其中4賊攜巨款駕乘七人車逃去，另4人徒步逃逸。警方採取「捷進」行動及鎖定賊車資料，於大半小時後在美孚行車天橋截獲賊車，車上4賊棄車逃走，其中兩人跳橋逃走，警方一輪追捕，擒獲其中3人，並起回失款，目前正通緝其餘賊人。"},{"pid":"7a1817765a5064d8e4c389c1bb75ffa2b6685ed7","tid":557192,"uid":136455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T06:14:40.000Z","msg":"蝻: 多謝雄哥帶我過黎搵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a9814116208d9e1dfa69dfe2f337bca45a40cf4","tid":557192,"uid":136455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T02:14:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0312a66c3b19c33165852f128736c8305c2e83ae","tid":557192,"uid":136455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-12T06:41:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}